// Kodex Store
// Zustand store for managing the selected project and the registered projects list for the Kodex knowledge base.

State shape:
  selectedProject: string | null  (absolute path)
  projects: Project[]
  isLoadingProjects: boolean
  projectsError: string | null

FUNCTION setSelectedProject(path)                                       EXPORT
  Set selectedProject to path and clear any error.

---

FUNCTION setProjects(projects)                                          EXPORT
  Set projects list and clear any error.

---

FUNCTION setLoadingProjects(loading)                                    EXPORT
  Set isLoadingProjects flag.

---

FUNCTION setProjectsError(error)                                        EXPORT
  Set projectsError message.

---

FUNCTION fetchProjects() -> Promise<void>                               EXPORT
  CALLS: list (projects-api)
  Set loading = true.
  Call projectsApi.list() to fetch all registered projects.
  On success: store the projects list and clear loading/error.
  On failure: store the error message and clear loading.

---

FUNCTION addProject(path) -> Promise<boolean>                           EXPORT
  CALLS: register (projects-api), fetchProjects (kodexStore)
  Call projectsApi.register(path).
  IF registration fails, store error and return false.
  Refresh the projects list by calling fetchProjects.
  Auto-select the newly added project.
  Return true on success, false on failure.

---

FUNCTION removeProject(path) -> Promise<boolean>                        EXPORT
  CALLS: unregister (projects-api), fetchProjects (kodexStore)
  Call projectsApi.unregister(path).
  IF removal fails, store error and return false.
  IF the removed project was the selected one, clear selectedProject.
  Refresh the projects list by calling fetchProjects.
  Return true on success, false on failure.

---

FUNCTION reset()                                                        EXPORT
  Reset all state to initial values: no selection, empty list, no loading, no error.
